*--------------------------------( Misc: Skin )------------------------------*

   Type:        command
   Usage:       skin <corpse>
                
   Description: You try to get the skin of a dead corpse with a sharp weapon.
		To make a succes you should be confident with the weapon
		and the fauna.
                
   Example:     skin corpse of a rat
   
